  "title": "Crawler Crane Operator",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Performing routine maintenance to ensure vehicle is clean and in good and safe conditions</li><li>Inspecting the crane to ensure its safety including cleaning and maintaining the crane hoisting mechanism</li><li>To lift, move and position materials at Construction Site</li><li>Comply to all safety rules and regulations</li><li>Other duties as and when assigned by the Superior</li></ul><p>Job Requirements</p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Cane Driver with a valid Class 4 driving licence</li><li>Min 2 years of relevant working experience</li><li>Possess a valid crawler crane certificate and safety certificate</li><li>Positive attitude, physically fit</li><li>Good driving skills and records</li></ul>",
